      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention; the engine has a persistent oil leak and a rough idle, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The body shows extensive wear, including significant rust spots on the rocker panels, several large dents, and faded paint across the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin shows its age with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and several non-functional electrical components, including the radio and rear power windows. This car is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source of spare parts, as it will need substantial repairs before it can be considered a reliable daily driver.",
