    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The engine runs consistently but would benefit from a tune-up, and the transmission is functional despite some occasional hesitation in lower gears. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver\u2019s seat and some light staining on the carpet. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections and minor upcoming maintenance needs.",
