    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S is a superlative example of lightweight engineering and rotary precision. It features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine, delivering a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The chassis remains factory-stiff, maintaining its renowned 50:50 weight distribution and double-wishbone suspension geometry. Every mechanical component, from the complex vacuum routing to the limited-slip differential, has been meticulously preserved to maintain original factory tolerances. The exterior finish and interior appointments are flawless, representing a true turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking peak JDM performance.",
      "price": 49500.0,
